{"word":"G1934 - ἐπιζητέω - epizētéō - ep-eed-zay-teh'-o - Desire","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιζητέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epizētéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-eed-zay-teh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Desire</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தேடு, ஆசையாயிரு, நாடு, விசாரி"},{"paragraph":"to inquire for, seek for, search for, seek diligently"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G2212 - ζητέω - zētéō - dzay-teh'-o/2212\">G2212</a>; to <i>search</i> (<i>inquire</i>) <i>for</i>; intensively to <i>demand</i>, to <i>crave:</i> - desire, enquire, seek (after, for).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}